		   Email: info@mandom.co.th
		</p>
<div class="respinsive-i">
  		<iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d1937.9717368279867!2d100.5292113!3d13.7218721!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0000000000000000%3A0x691ec387b1b9a142!2sMandom+Corporation+Ltd.!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sth!4v1561973275655!5m2!1sen!2sth" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
